episode of.title: Doctor Who: Parallel Eleventh Doctor (TV Series 2007– )

10.plot: Masses of technical machinery, tanks, weapons and warfare are being used to win a great war that has spanned hundreds of years. With the population wiped out, Commander Strunder had only one option left open to him - to clone himself and continue fighting. However, what he didn't take into consideration was - the ever growing weight of the weapons and complex machinery is having an adverse effect on the planet, causing it to be at critical level.
